data.description: If you're in search of a pristine two-story home with plenty of square footage, your search ends here! This charming home offers a formal living and dining area, as well as a spacious great room with a cozy gas log fireplace for relaxed evenings. Enjoy 9ft ceilings throughout the first floor.The great room connects to a delightful breakfast nook for casual dining, which looks out to the backyard patio. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, a pantry, prep island, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. There are four generously sized bedrooms, with the primary suite featuring a stunning vaulted ceiling and a large walk-in closet. The primary bath includes an oversized shower, garden tub, and dual vanities. Bedrooms 2, 3, and 4 are spacious with ample closet space. Additionally, there's a versatile loft area, a two-car garage, tankless gas hot water heater, and a fully fenced backyard. Experience the convenience of nearby shopping, parks, and easy highway access. Qualifies for USDA loan based on current mapping.
